{"tid":1815764,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港共點解唔應對武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-07T18:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T12:57:37.000Z","uid":227447,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7afafbce6b6ccc22b301621acf814ff52cefe8af","tid":1815764,"uid":227447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:24:42.000Z","msg":"傻嘅都知咩事，支那已經做緊檢疫措施，連奧門都有做，香港班仆街點會傻都知咩事啦<br />\n陰謀論咁講，<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我覺得係港共特登想今次個疫症係香港爆發</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n一來賭疫症可能令我地唔再型遊行，就算拉唔曬都加大個疫症嘅傳播機會<br />\n<br />\n二來當怕左個疫症，啲人少咗出門口，一靜落嚟方便佢地清算<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>各位手足</ins></strong></span></span>要做好衛生防疫嘅工作，口罩，消毒酒精，要用就用。<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>區議員</ins></strong></span></span></strong>，唔該做下野，迫下啲仆街政府同管理處個啲保安加強防疫工作！"},{"pid":"3a6d1146f24083825624e9176fbdeb06399c5f2c","tid":1815764,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqbaiDe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqbaiDe.jpg&h=eeece8c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8b2dc3ab6f8a1190af84827a4d460b9ffd62f76","tid":1815764,"uid":227447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6d1146f24083825624e9176fbdeb06399c5f2c","tid":1815764,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqbaiDe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqbaiDe.jpg&h=eeece8c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:08:32.000Z","msg":"去開成人台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d72c49b6908b79590a35e9a101de636cda410fb","tid":1815764,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime